author: Rachel Bachman
title: Ester Ledecka Wins Gold in Super G; Lindsey Vonn Finishes 6th
text:
JEONGSEONG, South Korea—Lindsey Vonn’s 2018 Winter Olympics started Saturday with a sixth-place finish, not the kind of glory for which history’s most accomplished female Alpine skier risks life and limb.
But after missing the 2014 Games with an injury, the 33-year-old Vonn said she was thrilled to be back.
